dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the city of Plainfield, Union County, and borough of North Plainfield, Somerset County, New Jersey (Sheet 28)
dct_description_sm: Includes key, streets and specials index, and text. "2952." Preliminary sheet [3] has title: Map of congested district of Plainfield, N.J. Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-8, 11-17, 23, and 25-66; sheets 9-10, 18-22, and 24, showing North Plainfield, foldered separately.
